            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped veg</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for 10-12 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 50ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [75ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
