            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a separate baking tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong> and unwrap your <strong>puff pastry </strong>and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>rolled pastry</strong> to the tray, then prick the inside of the pastry all over with a fork (this will stop you from getting a soggy bottom!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1658234661837-x200.jpg",
