        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the galette is cooking, wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> to a medium bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>chopped basil </strong>to the bowl and toss – this is your <strong>herby salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
