    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> ratatouille galette</strong> in half and tear over the<strong> reserved basil leaves</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>ratatouille galette </strong>with the<strong> herby salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
